# Keep the harness, not its output.
#
# Each run dir is an isolated repo assembled by make-run.sh (it runs `git init`
# inside itself, so committing it would create a stray gitlink), plus its shim
# state and the review artifacts publish.py derives from them. All of it is
# reproducible: ./setup-iteration.sh N and re-run the agents.
iteration-*/
skill-snapshot-*/

# scratch state from tools invoked with this directory as cwd
.agentqa/
*.log
__pycache__/
